      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td><strong>作者</strong></td>
          <td>Gabriel Tseng, Anthony Fuller, Marlena Reil, Henry Herzog, Patrick Beukema, Favyen Bastani, James R. Green, Evan Shelhamer 等</td>
